{
  "id": "69f1b903ba480e16843f610c",
  "title": "丸亀製麺のうどん札を集める会",
  "created": 1777449220,
  "updated": 1777803810,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f1b903ba480e16843f610c",
      "text": "丸亀製麺のうどん札を集める会",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449220,
      "updated": 1777449220
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9030000000000358b23",
      "text": "from [2026/04/29]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449220,
      "updated": 1777449220
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9030000000000358b24",
      "text": "[丸亀製麺]の[うどん札]を集める会",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449220,
      "updated": 1777449227
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b90f0000000000358b27",
      "text": "書いとかないとうどん札の存在を忘れるのでページを作ってしまった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449232,
      "updated": 1777449249
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9030000000000358b25",
      "text": " 4/29 1枚もらった[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449220,
      "updated": 1777449220
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1bc150000000000cfd0ac",
      "text": " これのリマインダって何か作れるんかな[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777450006,
      "updated": 1777450014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1bc230000000000cfd0ad",
      "text": " \t月末に毎回「うどん札溜まってませんか？」って通知が来るようにすればいいのか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777450019,
      "updated": 1777450051
    },
    {
      "id": "69f71fb90000000000a083e4",
      "text": " \tむずそう[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777803193,
      "updated": 1777803207
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7220e0000000000a083ea",
      "text": " \t たしかに定期的に通知すればよいものというのはありそう",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777803790,
      "updated": 1777803806
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7203a0000000000a083e6",
      "text": "  \t 月末にまとめて通知すればいいもの",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777803322,
      "updated": 1777803810
    },
    {
      "id": "69f721fe0000000000a083e7",
      "text": "  \t 週末に",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777803774,
      "updated": 1777803810
    },
    {
      "id": "69f722030000000000a083e8",
      "text": "  \t 日の終わりに",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777803779,
      "updated": 1777803810
    },
    {
      "id": "69f722060000000000a083e9",
      "text": "  \t ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777803783,
      "updated": 1777803810
    },
    {
      "id": "69f71f7700000000002f160d",
      "text": " 5/3 もらた[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777803128,
      "updated": 1777803134
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9830000000000358b28",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449348,
      "updated": 1777449348
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9830000000000358b29",
      "text": ">[「うどん札」を集めた時の特典を教えてください。 https://jp.marugame.com/faq/]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449348,
      "updated": 1777449375
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9850000000000358b2a",
      "text": "> 次回以降のご来店時に、集めた枚数によって以下の特典をご利用いただけます。",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449349,
      "updated": 1777449349
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9850000000000358b2b",
      "text": "> 3枚で「トッピングひとつ無料」（大根おろし・とろろ・明太子・すだち※　より一品）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449349,
      "updated": 1777449349
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9850000000000358b2c",
      "text": "> 5枚で「天ぷら100円引き」（お好きな天ぷらを割引価格にてご提供）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449349,
      "updated": 1777449349
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9850000000000358b2d",
      "text": "> 10枚で「うどん(並)一杯無料」（ざる・かけ・ぶっかけ　より一品）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449349,
      "updated": 1777449349
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9850000000000358b2e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449349,
      "updated": 1777449379
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9030000000000358b26",
      "text": "もらった月の次の月の末日がそのうどん札の有効期限っぽい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777449220,
      "updated": 1777449434
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b9c50000000000358b2f",
